github.setup        Helvesec rmux 0.3.1 v
github.tarball_from archive
revision            0

description         Local terminal multiplexer with a tmux-style CLI

long_description    \
    RMUX is a local terminal multiplexer with a tmux-style CLI, daemon \
    runtime, Rust SDK, and ratatui integration. It supports detachable \
    terminal sessions, persistent panes, structured snapshots, and native \
    local transports on macOS.

